ath":"/2ZbrTPGB9252SuSQZun1W1adz2D.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":2812,"height":1582,"file_path":"/s07rVPqba0ivC3Pm286JLQEGMj0.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-26T04:14:36.61+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"롬","runtime":79,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"북적이는 도시 사이공의 뒷골목에서 벌어지는 욕망의 세계를 그리고 있다. 어렸을 때 부모에게 버림받은 롬은 부모의 행방을 알아내기 위해 돈을 모으려고 한다. 그의 직업은 전문적으로 숫자를 골라서 복권을 대리구매해주는 중계인이다. 행운의 숫자를 알아내기 위해 비과학적인 온갖 미신스러운 방법을 동원하며 다른 경쟁자가 상권에 진입하지 못하게 관리도 해야한다. 판을 키운 불법 복권의 세계에서 당첨이 되면 의뢰인으로부터 짭짤한 수수료를 받지만, 낙첨되면 의뢰인들의 항의에 도망다니기 바쁘다. 복잡하게 연결된 가운데 나름의 질서를 가지고 있는 슬럼가는 도시 재개발 계획으로 철거의 운명에 처하고, 골목 사람들은 집문서까지 내걸며 마지막 한탕을 노리는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“Rom”, trata sobre la vida de niños callejeros en la bulliciosa Ciudad  Ho Chi Minh, quienes intentan ayudar a los residentes en un antiguo condominio a mantener sus hogares y cumplir el sueño de encontrar a sus padres."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Rom","runtime":79,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"14-year-old Ròm works as bookie lottery runner to earn a living. He lives an unsettling life due to his separation from his parents and always yearns to earn enough money to find them."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Ròm","runtime":79,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Lấy bối cảnh một khu chung cư cũ đang chờ giải tỏa tại Sài Gòn, Ròm kể câu chuyện về cuộc sống của những người dân lao động nơi đây. Họ đều chơi số đề với hy vọng kiếm được một khoản tiền lớn để đổi đời. Ròm là cậu bé làm “cò đề” để kiếm sống qua ngày, chuyên tư vấn cho người dân những con số may mắn để họ có cơ may trúng đề."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Ром","runtime":79,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ром, молодой букмекер из шумного Сайгона, старается изо всех сил помочь жителям старого жилого комплекса сохранить свои дома и осуществить свою мечту — найти своих родителей."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"人性爆走課","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在經濟呈爆炸性發展的胡志明市，孤兒少年細漢盡一切所能在猶如越南九龍城寨的底層求生存。靠著幫當地居民報明牌、投注樂透維生，但面對虎視眈眈想都更的各路奸商黑幫，被逼至絕境的他必須為自己殺出一條生路。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"瘦弱少年","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":380762,"adult":false,"title":"Trivisa","video":false,"overview":"Hong Kong's three notorious thieves who have never met one another before appear in the same restaurant. This leads to a rumour that they are joining forces to pull off something big before the Handover, though this is not something that any of them.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9173,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/jhsLDrUx1Oc22daT5GBnhsD53CJ.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-07","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/jbWbUmVxcUQDWK7HXHnzyIb9pb8.jpg","original_title":"樹大招風","original_language":"cn"},{"id":997519,"adult":false,"title":"Arnold Is a Model Student","video":false,"overview":"Arnold is a clever student who has won many academic awards. One day, he meets Bee who has an underground business of helping students to cheat their exams. Bee asks Arnold to join his cheating ring and offers him a lot of money. While Arnold is considering working with Bee, at his school, many students are not happy with the school’s disrespect of their freedom and they organize a big protest.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0844,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/dxDlxbf3kFOMFw8ZQ3j94hloumt.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-09","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/lz7PNCdvkeUJ2QnGe3t6Zm8XSTj.jpg","original_title":"อานนเป็นนักเรียนตัวอย่าง","original_language":"th"},{"id":181812,"adult":false,"title":"Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker","video":false,"overview":"The surviving Resistance faces the First Order once again as the journey of Rey, Finn and Poe Dameron continues. With the power and knowledge of generations behind them, the final battle begins.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.0801,"vote_count":10634,"poster_path":"/db32LaOibwEliAmSL2jjDF6oDdj.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-18","vote_average":6.273,"backdrop_path":"/jOzrELAzFxtMx2I4uDGHOotdfsS.jpg","original_title":"Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker","original_language":"en"},{"id":640154,"adult":false,"title":"Comidark Films: In Between","video":false,"overview":"Working in a ferry as a waiter, Ayzek, having a defect with his front teeth, dreams to get his front teeth fixed and to marry his girlfriend, Songül. The news gets out that the ferry company is turning over the management to a new one and the whole crew is to be interviewed. When the interviewer arrives on board, Ayzek’s world is turned upside down.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.224,"vote_count":102,"poster_path":"/6eOFH9Ib9ZMDf5W7gczM9rUNk0v.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-18","vote_average":6.387,"backdrop_path":"/jGVqlfMuVEM91hzUUOdOI4CLFg5.jpg","original_title":"Karakomik Filmler: 2 Arada","original_language":"tr"},{"id":564147,"adult":false,"title":"K.G.F: Chapter 1","video":false,"overview":"A period drama set in the 1970s, KGF follows the story of a fierce rebel who rises against the brutal oppression in Kolar Gold Fields and becomes the symbol of hope to legions of downtrodden people.","genre_ids":[28,53,12,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1386,"vote_count":264,"poster_path":"/ltHlJwvxKv7d0ooCiKSAvfwV9tX.jpg","