nkind watches as King Ghidorah, clad in a golden light, descends on the planet. The heavens and earth shake once again as the war moves to a higher dimension.","genre_ids":[16,878,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.7546,"vote_count":392,"poster_path":"/fOA44BITFth0u4hMSOUgpK0kM6t.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-09","vote_average":6.52,"backdrop_path":"/q3j4OQFFDKM6fdQt9gE56kfDBNG.jpg","original_title":"GODZILLA 星を喰う者","original_language":"ja"},{"id":641662,"adult":false,"title":"Pieces of a Woman","video":false,"overview":"When a young mother's home birth ends in unfathomable tragedy, she begins a year-long odyssey of mourning that fractures relationships with loved ones in this deeply personal story of a woman learning to live alongside her loss.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1905,"vote_count":1287,"poster_path":"/OgUfLlhfBFx5BPK6LzBWFvBW1w.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-30","vote_average":7.02,"backdrop_path":"/izNpxVcjKbF9BiYF4GVqxCOfewL.jpg","original_title":"Pieces of a Woman","original_language":"en"},{"id":404733,"adult":false,"title":"Overdrive","video":false,"overview":"Master car thieves square off against French gangsters in the South of France with money, women and lives all on the line.","genre_ids":[53,28,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3972,"vote_count":992,"poster_path":"/a0hTRjis1cxwmjOuBaS7WdDG3dj.jpg","release_date":"2017-06-16","vote_average":6.081,"backdrop_path":"/ywMkKd0heYn5TOYykSNZnw5xqnh.jpg","original_title":"Overdrive","original_language":"en"},{"id":406385,"adult":false,"title":"I Can Quit Whenever I Want 2: Masterclass","video":false,"overview":"Pietro Zinni is asked by the police to revive the old gang to create a task force that will stop the spread of smart drugs.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2809,"vote_count":1239,"poster_path":"/hBQgBWtDym6E7Qem6uhbWJUUHW8.jpg","release_date":"2017-02-02","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/croyOm5E0cv5DQkdAx60YLtGg2X.jpg","original_title":"Smetto quando voglio - Masterclass","original_language":"it"},{"id":419704,"adult":false,"title":"Ad Astra","video":false,"overview":"The near future, a time when both hope and hardships drive humanity to look to the stars and beyond. While a mysterious phenomenon menaces to destroy life on planet Earth, astronaut Roy McBride undertakes a mission across the immensity of space and its many perils to uncover the truth about a lost expedition that decades before boldly faced emptiness and silence in search of the unknown.","genre_ids":[878,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.3359,"vote_count":7086,"poster_path":"/xBHvZcjRiWyobQ9kxBhO6B2dtRI.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-17","vote_average":6.124,"backdrop_path":"/duengnNbJdTdjR329SmAAJO4stC.jpg","original_title":"Ad Astra","original_language":"en"},{"id":642203,"adult":false,"title":"Seth Meyers: Lobby Baby","video":false,"overview":"SNL alumnus and subversive master of late-night Seth Meyers comes out from behind the desk to share some lighthearted stories from his own life.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1873,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/cOkN2Mfw76HkZRvS3kQqDeTqhrf.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-05","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/5NTE4ZyckTSKLjEMxRClKcqe2yK.jpg","original_title":"Seth Meyers: Lobby Baby","original_language":"en"},{"id":337401,"adult":false,"title":"Mulan","video":false,"overview":"When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Chinese Army to defend the country from Huns, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. She is spirited, determined and quick on her feet. Disguised as a man by the name of Hua Jun, she is tested every step of the way and must harness her innermost strength and embrace her true potential.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6287,"vote_count":6970,"poster_path":"/aKx1ARwG55zZ0GpRvU2WrGrCG9o.jpg","release_date":"2020-09-04","vote_average":6.837,"backdrop_path":"/zMrk2G3XsnfYKiIp1NEfdtvDyBH.jpg","original_title":"Mulan","original_language":"en"},{"id":299582,"adult":false,"title":"A Royal Christmas","video":false,"overview":"A young working girl with a blue-collar background is surprised when her new fiancé announces he is actually a prince of a small sovereign country in Europe. After the couple quickly takes off to spend the holidays at his family’s sprawling, royal castle, she must work hard to win over her disapproving and unaccepting future mother-in-law—the Queen—and find out if love truly can conquer all.","genre_ids":[10770,10749,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6053,"vote_count":248,"poster_path":"/r7wDZesIEdn9UJgqBLzulbFRhCr.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-21","vote_average":6.681,"backdrop_path":"/jijTbvaz8q8Fpega331tBFwQm3s.jpg","original_title":"A Royal Christmas","original_language":"en"},{"id":806643,"adult":false,"title":"This Little Love of Mine","video":false,"overview":"Laura Price is a successful San Francisco lawyer on the cusp of promotion – a far cry from her childhood growing up on a tropical island with best friends Chip and Gem. When the firm’s biggest client – Chip’s grandfather – asks Laura to travel to the island and deliver a contract to make Chip his heir, she leaves behind her practice and fiancé Owen to convince her childhood friend to sign a contract that will make him a billionaire.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6275,"vote_count":143,"poster_path":"/astp4qwuZlCPVzntnKivcVJTaJj.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-22","vote_average":6.063,"backdrop_path":"/bcOrEyXWxe4nnqcStQSOSRrl6z4.jpg","original_title":"This Little Love of Mine","original_language":"en"},{"id":429617,"adult":false,"title":"Spider-Man: Far From Home","video":false,"overview":"Peter Parker and his friends go on a summer trip to Europe. However, they will hardly be able to rest - Peter will have to agree to help Nick Fury uncover the mystery of creatures that cause natural disasters and destruction throughout the continent.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.8721,"vote_count":16704,"poster_path":"/4q2NNj4S5dG2RLF9CpXsej7yXl.jpg","release_date":"2019-06-28","vote_average":7.396,"backdrop_path":"/34jW8LvjRplM8Pv06cBFDpLlenR.jpg","original_title":"Spider-Man: Far From Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":733668,"adult":false,"title":"Return","video":false,"overview":"Eyüp decides to cross mount Ararat looking for his aunt in Yerevan after following a madman's words. His aunt has also been expecting someone to come from behind this mount for many years. Eyüp cannot be sure about the woman he finds behind the blue door, whether it is his aunt or not because they can't understand each other.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3064,"vote_count":424,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","vote_average":6.631,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Return","original_language":"hy"},{"id":513584,"adult":false,"title":"Think Like a Dog","video":false,"overview":"A 12-year-old tech prodigy, whose science experiment goes awry, forges a telepathic connection with his best friend, Henry-his dog! The duo join forces and use their unique perspectives on life to comically overcome complications of family and school.","genre_ids":[10751,35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7354,"vote_count":164,"poster_path":"/cDbOrc2RtIA37nLm0CzVpFLrdaG.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-06","vote_average":6.659,"backdrop_path":"/qEo36RiT8w4hMFlf9KohOSuX3HZ.jpg","original_title":"Think Like a Dog","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt11095810","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q71219955","instagram_id":null,"rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/rom"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148707,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":n